|              Assasian Help Disarm                    |  
|              ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~                    |    
|                                                      |
| Disarm will allow you to knock the weapon out of     |
| your foe's hands and at times drop it to the floor   |
| at your feet for easy pickens.                       |
|   Syntax: disarm <opponent> just disarm in combat    |
